com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport

Class LinkPlaceholder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.CoreItem
      • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.ItemPlaceholder
        • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.LinkPlaceholder

  • public final class LinkPlaceholder
extends ItemPlaceholder
    A placeholder for a Link that contains less information. A LinkPlaceholder is used in place of a Link when:
    • the Link has been deleted, or
    • the Link has been purged, or
    • the current user has only the SecurityAccessLevel.READ_CLOAKED access level on the Link, or
    • the current user has the SecurityAccessLevel.NONE access level and the SecurityGrantLevel.UPDATE grant level on the Link
    Since:
    1.0
